  "body": "### Description\n\nThe chunkSize used by the rest-client-reactive is currently a constant: https://github.com/quarkusio/quarkus/blob/cd3dece82a3f99ddc27ebcfca12c6b2e5018ee86/independent-projects/resteasy-reactive/client/runtime/src/main/java/org/jboss/resteasy/reactive/client/impl/multipart/QuarkusHttpPostBodyUtil.java#L31\r\n\r\nThere are cases (eg server not behaving properly) where being able to customize this size would help.\r\n\r\nWould it be possible to make this field customizable?\r\n\r\nRelevant tulip discussion: https://quarkusio.zulipchat.com/#narrow/stream/306418-resteasy-reactive/topic/deactivate.20chunked.20mode.20on.20the.20resteasy.20reactive.20client\n\n### Implementation ideas\n\nTransform the code to use a config property for the chunkSize value.",
